articles.title: OnePlus' new Nord includes a 108-megapixel camera and 67W fast charging - The Verge
articles.description: The OnePlus Nord CE 3 Lite cots €329 (£299) and will go on sale on April 20th in select markets across Europe and Asia but not the US. It offers 67W fast charging and has a main camera with a resolution of 108 megapixels.

articles.title: Maruti WagonR, Alto K10 score low safety rating in Global NCAP crash test - Economic Times
articles.description: Maruti Suzuki WagonR, Alto K10  scored zero stars for child occupant protection as per the Global NCAP's latest round of crash tests. Maruti, however, said its vehicles meet India's crash safety regulations which are almost similar to the standards in Europe.
